# Smart Planner App

## Description
This is a planner application that interacts with the JSONPlaceholder API to manage tasks.

## Features
- Fetch tasks (GET)
- Search tasks
- Pagination
- Add new tasks (POST)
- Update tasks (PATCH)
- Modular JavaScript structure
- Async/Await and Promises

## Technologies Used
- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript (ES6 Modules)
- Fetch API
- JSONPlaceholder API

## How to Run
Open index.html in a browser with Live Server.
